nodes.text: Raol was a Jazbinan resistance fighter for the Rebel Alliance and lover of Princess Syayna.

Raol assisted during the battle against Darth Vader and his stormtroopers on Jazbina with Luke Skywalker. He first housed jealousy against Luke, in the thought that he was trying to take Syayna from him.
